OL,3,CHundreds take part in Selkirk run for
OL,4,CBorders charity worker
OL,6,FHundreds of runners took part in a fun
OL,7,Frun in memory of a Borders charity
OL,8,Fworker in on Saturday.
OL,10,FPeople in the town donned their
OL,11,Ftrainers for The Interest Links
OL,12,FCharmian Challenge, which included a
OL,13,F5k trail run as well as a 2k and 4k
OL,14,Fwalk around the Haining.
OL,16,FCharmian Ledsham regularly gave her
OL,17,Ftime to volunteer at Interest Links
OL,18,FBorders helping those with learning
OL,19,Fdisabilities, before she took her own
OL,20,Flife two years ago.
