OL,3,CHundreds take part in Selkirk run for
OL,4,CBorders charity worker
OL,6,FArran Ledsham: "My mum was very much a
OL,7,Fgiver so she was someone who loved to
OL,8,Fconnect with people at all levels. She
OL,9,Floved to have a chat to anyone, she
OL,10,Freally listened.
OL,12,F"I think that idea of having a
OL,13,Fmeaningful connection people between
OL,14,Fpeople was what she was all about, so
OL,15,Fthat's what today is all about as well
OL,16,Fwhich is fantastic."
OL,18,FOne participant who knew Charmian told
OL,19,FITV Border that knowing Charmian
OL,20,Fpersonally made the event even more
OL,21,Fspecial for her.
